2221. Find Triangular Sum of an Array

Input: 
nums = [1,2,3,4,5]
Output: 
8

code:
class Solution:
    def triangularSum(self, nums: List[int]) -> int:
        while len(nums) > 1:
            a=[]
            for i in range(len(nums) - 1):
                value = (nums[i] + nums[i+1]) % 10
                a.append(value)
            nums=a
        return nums[0]
